{noformat}
000003b0  30 30 0d 00 0d 0a 61 3d  66 6d 74 70 3a 31 38 20  |00....a=fmtp:18 |
000003c0  61 6e 6e 65 78 62 3d 6e  6f 0d 00 0d 0a 61 3d 72  |annexb=no....a=r|
{noformat}

And I want to highlight or colorize "6f 0d 00 0d". Currently I don't know of any way to do this.

